{"tid":2247181,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)復活蛋","createTime":"2020-10-17T15:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T20:44:41.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"15f8b483dc23e1dc10c584182546861e6f8cde88","tid":2247181,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T15:38:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=e446a4ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=7279e977\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=1f42f2ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c3/Alien_movie_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc3%2FAlien_movie_poster.jpg&h=58e3e478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一架載有7名船員、名叫Nostromo的商業星際運載船，正將2千萬噸礦物由Thedus行星運送回地球。在電影開始時，被船員稱為母親的太空船電腦MU-TH-R 182收到一個來自鄰近星球、無法解析的訊號。「母親」將正在冬眠狀態的船員們喚醒，使他們能夠去偵察訊號的來源。醒來的船員們把礦物及提煉設施留在行星軌道，用Nostromo的拖曳用太空船登陸該星球，但機體被粗糙的星球表面造成了部份損壞........<br />\n<br />\n2.在電影的一開始，第一集中Nostromo的唯一一個人類生還者&mdash;&mdash;陸軍少尉艾倫&middot;雷普利（Ellen Ripley，雪歌妮&middot;薇佛），在太空獲救，並於57年的超睡眠後甦醒過來。醒來後，由於Ripley爆破了Nostromo，為了釐清責任，因此她的僱主Weyland-Yutani公司舉行了聽證會。由於沒有確切的物理證據証明在Nostromo摧毀時有不明生物存在，因此她的證詞被所有人懷疑而不被採信，而最後也因為她的「可疑的決定」，公司撤銷了Ripley的太空飛行執照......<br />\n<br />\n3.在上一部《異形3》中的故事200年後，死去的Ripley被軍方和公司的科學家復製出來，並成功地從其腹中取出了一具異形。而Ripley的基因里也帶上了異形的基因，使得她變得更加強壯。但是異形超強的繁殖能力和生長速度以及超乎想像的智慧，使得局勢很快失去控制。異形逃出了豢養它們的牢籠，在太空船上大開殺戒。為了不讓這些嗜血成性的生物來到地球上，Ripley必須想方設法殺死自己的「骨肉」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n11 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=0197e9e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=b7ae935f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f49bcbc10f1f61e4acf82fb8b0a4fe78fb39bf1","tid":2247181,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T15:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522dfec0d859dc0135ac7ef783c22bfc4f93050c","tid":2247181,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cfd8c2de0c1f760ef9f45261e578006c53fc65e","tid":2247181,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c80ab3f12966debb0ddd708f214289737142a0d","tid":2247181,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T20:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}